headline: McDonald's, Burger King, Wendy's rival closing more restaurants
summary: Both Burger King and Wendy's have closed, or plan to close, hundreds of restaurants. In the case of Burger King, the company has suffered from the loss of key franchise operators. That's something the chain mitigated by buying some of the closed locations, but it has lost dozens of restaurants. ...
